	o FLEXplorer: Inplace editor for filename and attributes
	o FLEXplorer: Confirmation to continue (Yes/No) when opening multiple
	  container files at once fails
	o FLEXplorer: Attributes dialog for displaying and modifying attributes
	  for one or multiple files
	o FLEXplorer: Windows menu for easy MDI window navigation
	o FLEXplorer: Window background has a bitmap
	o Most used menu items also available in toolbar
	o Detailed status messages in status bar
	o Linux: Add desktop files to System category (was in Games)
	o Add mime types for *.dsk, *.flx and *.wta files
	o flexemu:Toggle smooth screen
	o flexemu: When resizing always keep emulated screen aspect ratio
	o flexemu: Add keyboard documentation

Bug Fixes:
	o FileContainerIterator: Avoid potential dangling pointer
	o dsktool: Automatic text file con. one space is converted to $09 $01,
	  should be $20
	o Only open files needed for current config (Eurocom II/V5 or V7)
	o Only add floppy disk status buttons for Eurocom II/V7
	o autotools: Add missing build dependencies

Code Maintenance:
	o Support c++14 standard
	o configure option --disable-post-install to supress post installation
	  steps

